Jayendran,


Thank you for your note, and for your interest in Enron's Associate / Analyst Program.  I've copied Traci Warner who leads Recruiting for our Program.  Traci, or someone from her team will follow up with you.


I've also noted your unique mix of weather / climate training and experience, combined with your financial analysis and risk management background.  We will highlight this experience with a couple of specific groups.


Please let me know if I can be of further assistance.


Best regards,

Billy Lemmons

