Please find attached my resume and a cover letter stating my interest in the

Associate program at Enron. I look forward to discussing with you soon my

interest in Enron.


At the Johnson School, I am building on my financial analysis and risk

management skills as a portfolio manager in the $2 million Cayuga MBA Fund,

